Class Demon

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mygdx.game.Enemy
      • com.mygdx.game.Demon

  • public class Demon
extends Enemy
    Big red boss monster, fires in rapid bursts of 3 projectiles, chases the player and then periodically charges towards the player.
    Author:
    Sean Aubrey, Gabriel Fountain, Brandon Conn
